}{}-tego punktu o masie {OPENAGHMATHJAX()}\Delta {OPENAGHMATHJAX}m{OPENAGHMATHJAX()}_{i}{OPENAGHMATHJAX}
wynosi v{OPENAGHMATHJAX()}_{i}{OPENAGHMATHJAX} =
r{OPENAGHMATHJAX()}_{i}{OPENAGHMATHJAX}{OPENAGHMATHJAX()}\omega {OPENAGHMATHJAX} gdzie
r{OPENAGHMATHJAX()}_{i}{OPENAGHMATHJAX} jest odległością od osi obrotu}
